Develop and implementation of all safe works procedures, safety permit systems, in-house rules and regulation including all processes and all activities to manage and control safety and health risks
-Responsibility to advise occupier in accordance to the WSH legal requirement of the works performed. Assist in all coordination and carrying out all risk assessment activity
-Develop all emergency respond procedures and emergency rescue operations including all implementation during this circuit breaker covic-19.
-Implementation and update all compliance to alocal legislation, acts and regulations pertaining to workplace safety and health.
-Responsible in all administration and management of all company International Standard - Management System and its certification including all internal and external audit